{"title":"es5之前要获取当前函数本身","slug":"es5之前要获取当前函数本身","date":"2017-09-20T01:59:08.777Z","updated":"2017-09-12T13:07:56.402Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"es5之前要获取当前函数本身，可以在函数体内部通过arguments-callee\"><a href=\"#es5之前要获取当前函数本身，可以在函数体内部通过arguments-callee\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"es5之前要获取当前函数本身，可以在函数体内部通过arguments.callee\"></a>es5之前要获取当前函数本身，可以在函数体内部通过arguments.callee</h2></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>es5规定了严格模式，严格模式中禁止使用callee/caller</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在严格模式下面如何获取当前函数？</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div><div class=\"line\">5</div><div class=\"line\">6</div><div class=\"line\">7</div><div class=\"line\">8</div><div class=\"line\">9</div><div class=\"line\">10</div><div class=\"line\">11</div><div class=\"line\">12</div><div class=\"line\">13</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">(<span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">fn</span></span>()&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">    //fn是一个<span class=\"string\">\"特殊的名字\"</span>,这个名字在外界访问不是一个函数名，在函数体内部访问就指向函数本身</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;)()</div><div class=\"line\">``` </div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">+ 面试题</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\">```bash</div><div class=\"line\">var f1 = funtion <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"title\">f2</span></span>()&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">    console.log(f1 === f2)  //<span class=\"literal\">true</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">&#125;</div><div class=\"line\">console.log(typeof f1) //Function</div><div class=\"line\">console.log(typeof f2) //<span class=\"string\">\"untifined\"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":[{"name":"关于ES5规范","path":"api/categories/关于ES5规范.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"掉坑里了","path":"api/tags/掉坑里了.json"}]}